Invocation Name: country population
des:
Country population skill tells a random country of the world and its population in 2019.
Learn about countries that you have not heard about before!

To start say "Alexa, open country population". To hear more, tell "tell me another country".

Tell "exit" to exit the skill.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
